    "body": "### Problem\n\nWhen you do a `:help vim.lsp.buf.workspace_diagnostics()` then the URL mentioned in \"See Also\" section is incorrect.\n\nExpected:\n- https://microsoft.github.io/language-server-protocol/specifications/lsp/3.17/specification/#workspace_diagnostic\n\nActual:\n- https://microsoft.github.io/language-server-protocol/specifications/specification-current/#workspace_dagnostics\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n1. Open nvim\n2. `:help vim.lsp.buf.workspace_diagnostics()`\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nExpected:\n- https://microsoft.github.io/language-server-protocol/specifications/lsp/3.17/specification/#workspace_diagnostic\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nv0.12.2\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nNO\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nArchLinux\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nGhostty+Tmux\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nxterm-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nsystem package manager",
